                Intercollege Transfer
              











Architecture, Design, and the Arts
Intercollege Transfer Information Sessions






            CADA ICT
          Heading link



 
Copy link



In the College of Architecture, Design, and the Arts the academic advisors meet with prospective intercollege transfer students; therefore, we do not host Information Sessions. Although, the advisors prefer students to make an appointment they often will meet with walk-ins. Below you will find our current list of advisors and the areas they represent.

Maria Tolbert-Ross: Architecture dbljoy@uic.edu
Liv Jordan: Art, Art Education, Art History, and Interdisciplinary Educations in the Arts (IDEAS) ojordan2@uic.edu
Somya Garg: Graphic Design and Industrial Design sgarg26@uic.edu
Lisa Tang: Theatre and Music ltang9@uic.edu




      College of Architecture, Design, and the Arts
    
















 
